de8bf","tid":203164,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"難得大陸有篇野係正常合理<br />\n點知班生番居然發癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a24d606d6ec354c0df98fb3fce666165669d28","tid":203164,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題目出事啦，你改個題做沒文化遊客 40樣特點，你有嗎？ 咁就唔會玻璃心</blockquote><br />\n老子有的是錢<br />\n喜歡怎樣做就怎樣做<br />\n關你屁事"},{"pid":"3fb6446b1cd12cd85a29cfd46fac6b2cf2b66176","tid":203164,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:59:23.000Z","msg":"常識都要人教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}